quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  89,1,"M wẽen ne fagiri"
  89,2,"La M wẽen ne yʋnd piigã,"
  89,3,"La ne sõd-yiibu la lugum (sõd-yiib-n-tõatga)."
  89,4,"La ne yʋngã t'a sã n wa gũd kuidga."
  89,5,"Rẽ yĩnga yεl nins sẽn togsã, wẽeneg bee be n sek yam soab bɩ?"
  89,6,"Fo pa yã wãn-wãn la fo Soabã maan a ʿAad rãmba?"
  89,7,"ɭram rãmb sẽn yaa zeng-raad rãmba,"
  89,8,"B sẽn pa naan b bilgr tẽmsã pʋga?"
  89,9,"La Ṯamuud rãmb sẽn yaa neb nins sẽn pees pĩigã ko-soogẽ wã?"
  89,10,"La a Fɩr-ʿaoon sẽn yaa bay soabã?"
  89,11,"Sẽn maan-b n zʋʋg tẽmsã pʋga."
  89,12,"N wʋsg sãang a pʋgẽ."
  89,13,"Tɩ b Soabã kiig b zug naong kõbg toor-toore."
  89,14,"Ad fo Soabã yaa gũusda."
  89,15,"La sã n yaa ne ninsaala, a Soabã sã n wa zarb-a n na n gese, n waoog-a, n neem-a, la a sẽn yete: ""mam Soabã waooga maam""."
  89,16,"La A sã n wa zarb-a, n weoog a rɩtlã a zugu, la a sẽn yete: ""mam Soabã yaala maam""."
  89,17,"Pa woto ye! Y pa waoogd kɩɩb ye."
  89,18,"Y leb n pa pirsd taab ne ninbãan-neb rɩlgr ye."
  89,19,"La y rɩt faadã ne kãas-n-rɩ."
  89,20,"La y nong arzεkã nong-kεgenga."
  89,21,"Pa woto ye! Lɑk Tẽn-gãngã sã n wa rãmb rãmbg tεkẽ."
  89,22,"Tɩ fo Soabã wa, la malεgsã, rulg-rulga."
  89,23,"Tɩ b wa ne Gεhannem bɑ-rɑɑrã; ra-kãng raare ninsaal tẽegdame, la tẽegr bεε ne-a?"
  89,24,"A yetame: ""kɑeto, Mam sã n da maana neer tɩ reng taoore mam beoog vɩɩmã yĩnga, pɑ são""."
  89,25,"La ra-kãngã, ned pa namsd wala A namsgã buud ye."
  89,26,"Ned bɑ ɑ yembr me pa sẽbd wala A sẽbrã ye."
  89,27,"Yaa foo yõor sẽn tar bas-m-yam lɑ yĩn-yõgnego!"
  89,28,"Leb f Soabã nengẽ, tɩ f yaa sẽn yɑr-A n yɑɑ b sẽn yard-a soaba."
  89,29,"Bɩ f kẽ Mam yemb-sõmsã pʋgẽ."
  89,30,"La f kẽ Mam Arzãnã."
